WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.460 --> 00:00:04.370
In the same way that soap is used to kill bacteria by lysing, or

00:00:04.370 --> 00:00:06.370
breaking them open, dish soap will help

00:00:06.370 --> 00:00:09.150
to break open the strawberry cells. Additionally,

00:00:09.150 --> 00:00:11.900
the active ingredient in meat tenderizer, called

00:00:11.900 --> 00:00:16.110
bromelain, has proteolytic activities, or the ability

00:00:16.110 --> 00:00:18.400
to break down proteins, that will also

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:21.250
help rupture cell membranes and free the DNA.

